  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Sunday</td>
    <td colspan="2">9:30am to 12:30pm</td>
  </tr>
</table>
<h2>Appointments at another branch</h2>
<p>Registered patients can book appointments at the practice’s other surgery: Kenyon Medical Centres: Chace Avenue</p>
<h2>Same-day appointments</h2>
<p>Call reception at 8am Monday to Friday to see if a same-day appointment is available.</p>
<h2>Early morning appointments</h2>
<p>Book a week in advance for early morning appointments on Mondays, Wednesdays or Fridays, 7am to 7:50am</p>
<hr class="hr--full-width" style="margin:40px 0;">
<h2>Book a GP appointment</h2>
<p><a href="{{gp.organisation_code}}/book-appointment">Book an appointment with a GP</a></p>
<hr class="hr--full-width" style="margin:40px 0;">
<h2>What patients say about this surgery</h2>
<p>The GP Patient Survey is an annual survey that shows what patients think of their surgery.</p>
<p>The table below shows some of the latest results for this surgery.</p>
<table class="table--grey">
  <tr>
    <th>&nbsp;</th>
    <th>This surgery</th>
    <th>National average</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Patients who would recommend their surgery</th><td>76%</td><td>78%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Patients who think the receptionists are helpful</th><td>82%</td><td>87%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Patients who said it’s easy to get through to this surgery on the phone</th><td>75%</td><td>73%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Patients who said booking an appointment was a good experience</th><td>66%</td><td>73%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Patients who had confidence in the last GP they saw</th><td>99%</td><td>95%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
